name: At Home Canada 2011 Tax Return
summary: Learn about .H11 files and view a list of programs that open them.

windows.name: Open over 400 file formats with File Viewer Plus.Free Download

content: The H11 file extension is used by the 2011 version of At Home Canada, so H11 files are generally created in 2012. H11 files can be opened directly by the Canadian version of At Home and may be imported by the Canadian version of TurboTax.
NOTE: H&R Block Canada At Home became H&R Block Canada Tax Software in 2013.

description: Tax return created with H&R Block Canada's At Home tax preparation software; includes Canadian income tax forms and personal tax data entered by the user; used to save the progress of a tax return so it can be opened and resumed at a later time.
